'''2016年3月伊斯坦布尔爆炸案'''是指于2016年3月19日发生在[[土耳其|土耳其]][[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]市中心附近[[塔克西姆广场|塔克西姆广场]][[独立大街|独立大街]]的自杀性炸弹袭击事件。袭击发生地附近是游客密集的购物区，爆炸地点紧邻当地地区行政長官办公室。此次爆炸造成包括袭击者本人在内的五人死亡，另有36人受伤，其中12人为外籍游客。<ref name="The Guardian">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/mar/19/istanbul-hit-by-deadly-bomb-attack|title=Istanbul hit by suicide attack|work=[[卫报|The Guardian]]|date=2016-03-19|accessdate=2016-06-18|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629142349/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/mar/19/istanbul-hit-by-deadly-bomb-attack|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="al jazeera">{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/03/istanbul-taksim-square-area-hit-explosion-160319091702737.html|title=Istanbul bombing: At least five killed in Turkish city|work=[[半岛电视台|Al Jazeera]]|date=2016-03-20|accessdate=2016-06-18|archive-date=2016-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628212821/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/03/istanbul-taksim-square-area-hit-explosion-160319091702737.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>土耳其警方在调查后确认此次袭击由该国本土出生的男子穆罕默德·奧茲圖爾克（{{lang|tr|Mehmet Öztürk}}）发动，袭击与[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]有关<ref name="CNN ISIS">{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/03/19/europe/turkey-blast/|title=Istanbul explosion: Suicide bomber had ISIS links, says Turkey's interior minister|work=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=2016-03-20|accessdate=2016-06-18|archive-date=2016-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160607003834/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/03/19/europe/turkey-blast/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NYT ISIS">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/21/world/middleeast/istanbul-suicide-bombing-turkey-isis.html|title=Turkish Member of ISIS Carried Out Istanbul Bombing, Official Says|work=[[纽约时报|New York Times]]|date=2016-03-20|accessdate=2016-06-18|archive-date=2016-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160608142716/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/21/world/middleeast/istanbul-suicide-bombing-turkey-isis.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Hurriyet">{{cite news|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/bombaci-mehmet-ozturkun-kardesi-anlatti-camide-namaz-kilmazdi-40074704|title=Bombacı Mehmet Öztürk'ün kardeşi anlattı: Camide namaz kılmazdı|work=Hurriyet|date=2016-03-24|accessdate=2016-06-18|language=tr|archive-date=2016-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160703081230/http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/bombaci-mehmet-ozturkun-kardesi-anlatti-camide-namaz-kilmazdi-40074704|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CNN Turk">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnnturk.com/video/turkiye/taksim-bombacisi-mehmet-ozturk-kamerada|title=Taksim bombacısı Mehmet Öztürk kamerada|work=CNN Türk|date=2016-03-21|accessdate=2016-06-18|language=tr|archive-date=2016-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624014829/http://www.cnnturk.com/video/turkiye/taksim-bombacisi-mehmet-ozturk-kamerada|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
土耳其位于[[中东|中东]]和[[欧洲|欧洲]]交界，紧邻[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]，介入[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]后安全形势高度紧张<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-34503388|title=Turkey violence: How dangerous is instability?|work=BBC|date=2016-06-07|accessdate=2016-06-18|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629102752/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-34503388|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该国靠近[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]控制地区，境内亦有[[库尔德人|库尔德人]]反政府武装，自2015年底起便频频遭遇恐怖袭击<ref name="al jazeera"/><ref name="Independent">{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/istanbul-explosion-injuries-reported-as-tourist-shopping-area-hit-by-blast-in-turkish-city-a6940706.html|title=Istanbul explosion: At least five dead as tourist shopping area Istiklal Street hit by suicide bombing in Turkey|work=[[独立报|The Independent]]|date=2016-03-19|accessdate=2016-06-18|archive-date=2016-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320075504/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/istanbul-explosion-injuries-reported-as-tourist-shopping-area-hit-by-blast-in-turkish-city-a6940706.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年10月，土耳其首都[[安卡拉|安卡拉]]一天之内接连发生[[2015年安卡拉爆炸案|两起爆炸]]，超过100人丧生<ref name="BBC"/>；2016年1月，伊斯坦布尔遭到伊斯兰国成员发动的[[2016年1月伊斯坦布尔爆炸事件|自杀性爆炸袭击]]，造成至少12名德国游客死亡；2月，[[库尔德工人党|库尔德工人党]]在安卡拉发动[[2016年2月安卡拉爆炸案|炸弹袭击]]导致66人死亡；<ref name="reuters">{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-blast-idUSKCN0WL0D5|title=Suicide bomber kills four, wounds 36 in Istanbul shopping district|work=[[路透社|Reuters]]|date=2016-03-20|accessdate=2016-06-18|archive-date=2016-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160618115634/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkey-blast-idUSKCN0WL0D5|dead-url=no}}</ref>此次袭击近一周之前的3月13日，安卡拉{{le|2016年3月安卡拉爆炸案|March 2016 Ankara bombing|再次遇袭}}，一支库尔德军事武装{{le|库尔德自由之鹰|Kurdistan Freedom Falcons}}在市区引爆汽车炸弹，造成37人身亡<ref name="CNN ISIS"/><ref name="BBC">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-35850625|title=Istanbul shopping area hit by suicide bomber|work=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2016-03-19|accessdate=2016-06-18|archive-date=2016-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320135113/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-35850625|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此次爆炸是2016年以来土耳其遭受的第四次类似袭击<ref name="NYT ISIS"/>。

由于恐怖袭击事件频发，各国都对土耳其的安全状况表示担忧，美国和欧洲各国驻土耳其大使馆在2016年都曾对本国公民发布安全警示<ref>{{cite news|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-turkey-security-idUKKCN0WK0PB|title=Bomb kills policeman in southeast Turkey, embassies warn on security|work=Reuters|date=2016-03-18|accessdate=2016-06-18|archive-date=2016-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809032612/http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-turkey-security-idUKKCN0WK0PB|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/turkey-ankara-embassy-terror-warning_us_56e6f1f3e4b0b25c91829f16|title=Turks Eye US Embassy’s Terror Warning, Issued Two Days Before Ankara Attack, With Suspicion|work=[[赫芬顿邮报|Huffington Post]]|date=2016-03-14|accessdate=2016-06-18|archive-date=2016-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160616155918/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/turkey-ankara-embassy-terror-warning_us_56e6f1f3e4b0b25c91829f16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="reuters"/>。安卡拉汽车炸弹袭击后，土耳其各大城市的市民都提高了警惕<ref name="BBC"/>。3月17日，位于[[独立大街|独立大街]]附近的{{Link-de|德国驻伊斯坦布尔总领事馆|Deutsches Generalkonsulat Istanbul}}接到“非常可信的”恐怖袭击警告，在17日和18日两天因“安全原因”闭馆，{{Link-de|伊斯坦布尔德国学校|Deutsche Schule Istanbul}}和{{Link-de|德國駐土耳其大使館|Deutsche Botschaft Ankara}}也临时关闭<ref name="The Guardian"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ft.com/fastft/2016/03/17/germany-closes-istanbul-consulate-after-terror-warning/|title=Germany closes Istanbul consulate after terror warning|work=[[金融时报_(英国)|Financial Times]]|date=2016-03-17|accessdate=2016-06-18|archive-date=2016-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160523193137/http://www.ft.com/fastft/2016/03/17/germany-closes-istanbul-consulate-after-terror-warning/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="DW warning">{{cite news|url=http://www.dw.com/en/germany-shuts-embassy-consulate-and-schools-in-turkey-on-very-concrete-tip-off/a-19121618|title=Germany shuts embassy, consulate and schools in Turkey on 'very concrete' tip-off|work=[[德国之声|Deutsch Welle]]|date=2016-03-17|accessdate=2016-06-18|archive-date=2016-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160625110853/http://www.dw.com/en/germany-shuts-embassy-consulate-and-schools-in-turkey-on-very-concrete-tip-off/a-19121618|dead-url=no}}</ref>，一名德国驻伊斯坦布尔的官员称这座城市已经“人人自危”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dw.com/en/terror-threat-leaves-everyone-scared-in-istanbul/a-19122435|title=Terror threat leaves 'everyone scared' in Istanbul|work=Deutsch Welle|date=2016-03-17|accessdate=2016-06-18|archive-date=2016-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624191936/http://www.dw.com/en/terror-threat-leaves-everyone-scared-in-istanbul/a-19122435|dead-url=no}}</ref>。时任[[土耳其总理|土耳其总理]][[艾哈迈德·达武特奥卢|艾哈迈德·达武特奥卢]]称这些预警是“正常的”，呼吁民众共同抵制恐怖情绪的蔓延<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cumhuriyet.com.tr/haber/siyaset/499700/Davutoglu_na_gore__Almanya_nin_Turkiye_de_teror_alarmi__normal.html|title=Davutoğlu'na göre 'Almanya'nın Türkiye'de terör alarmı' normal|work=Cumhuriyet|date=2016-03-17|accessdate=2016-06-18|language=tr|archive-date=2016-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160525112616/http://www.cumhuriyet.com.tr/haber/siyaset/499700/Davutoglu_na_gore__Almanya_nin_Turkiye_de_teror_alarmi__normal.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，伊斯坦布尔当地政府对德国提供的安全警告也未给予足够重视<ref name="BBC"/>。达武特奥卢在爆炸发生后也因此遭到批评<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cumhuriyet.com.tr/haber/turkiye/501034/Herkes_patlama_olacagini_biliyordu__onlenemedi.html|title=Herkes patlama olacağını biliyordu, önlenemedi|work=Cumhuriyet|date=2016-03-19|accessdate=2016-06-18|language=tr|archive-date=2016-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160527172659/http://www.cumhuriyet.com.tr/haber/turkiye/501034/Herkes_patlama_olacagini_biliyordu__onlenemedi.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="WSJ"/>。

== 经过 ==
爆炸发生于2016年3月19日当地时间上午11:00左右，袭击发生地[[独立大街|独立大街]]是伊斯坦布尔最繁华的地区，路边各国商店和餐馆林立，游客众多<ref name="The Guardian"/><ref name="al jazeera"/>，多国领事馆亦位于独立大街附近<ref name="reuters"/>。这一时间通常是游人最密集的时段<ref name="al jazeera"/>，但由于之前德国领事馆发布的恐怖袭击预警，爆炸前数日内该地区的游客已经比往常有所减少<ref name="DW warning"/>。事发时有众多游客正在街道上漫步，监控录像显示嫌疑人在人行道上的一群游客身旁引爆了身上的炸弹。爆炸地点紧邻当地地区行政长官办公室<ref name="The Guardian"/>，数百米外还有一辆警车长期驻守<ref name="reuters"/>。土耳其警方调查后认为袭击者原计划在人群更密集的地方引爆，但因惧怕警察而未能到达袭击目标处<ref name="Independent"/><ref name="reuters PKK"/>。目击者称现场听到巨大的爆炸声，附近建筑“像纸片一样摇晃”；监控录像中可以看到现场有人倒在地上，失去反应。<ref name="The Guardian"/><ref name="Independent"/>人群随即陷入混乱发出尖叫，数百名游客四散逃离<ref name="al jazeera"/><ref name="BBC"/>。有目击者称爆炸现场四处散落着铁钉和小铁球，专家认为是袭击者为增加杀伤力而在炸弹中加入<ref name="posta">{{cite news|url=http://www.posta.com.tr/turkiye/HaberDetay/Taksim-de-canli-bomba-saldirisi-.htm?ArticleID=333017|title=Taksim'de canlı bomba saldırısı!|work=Posta|date=2016-03-19|accessdate=2016-06-18|language=tr|archive-date=2016-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160622073055/http://www.posta.com.tr/turkiye/HaberDetay/Taksim-de-canli-bomba-saldirisi-.htm?ArticleID=333017|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方和医护人员在爆炸后迅速赶赴现场，同时派遣多架警用直升机和救护车驻守爆炸现场。警方封锁了整个[[塔克西姆广场|塔克西姆广场]]地区，街道上的游人也被疏散一空。<ref name="al jazeera"/><ref name="CNN ISIS"/>

